{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"title":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"15.0"},{"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"tvOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"16.0"},{"name":"visionOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"name":"watchOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"11.0"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents25OUDSCheckboxIndeterminateV","symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checkbox is a UI element that allows to select multiple options from a set of mutually non exclusive choices."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Checkbox that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a checkbox to be displayed."}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate\/init(selection:accessibilityLabel:isError:isReadOnly:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate\/init(selection:accessibilityLabel:tableName:bundle:isError:isReadOnly:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndete